        public MongoWarp()

      • MongoWarp

        public MongoWarp(Faction faction,
                 String name,
                 LazyLocation location,
                 boolean locked,
                 String password)
        Creates a new Warp with the given parameters. If locked is set to true, a NullPointerException will be thrown if the password is null.
        Parameters:
        faction - the faction that created the warp.
        name - the name of the warp.
        location - the location of the warp.
        locked - whether this warp is password locked or not.
        password - the password for this warp.
